title: [Sylvarraend Road]
description: The winding cobblestone road crosses through a dense section of forest.  The thickness of the trees drowns out any moon or starlight from above, rendering it near impossible to mark loose stones or deep grooves along the road.

The winding cobblestone road crosses through a dense section of forest.  Whatever ambient light filtering in from above is muted, causing long shadows to play over the road making it difficult to mark loose stones or deep grooves.
